## 5. Accessibility

### 5.1 Keyboard Navigation

**REGLA**: Todos los elementos interactivos deben ser navegables por teclado.

```javascript
<rect
  className="bar"
  tabIndex={0}
  role="button"
  aria-label={`${d.category}: ${d.value}`}
  onKeyDown={(e) => {
    if (e.key === 'Enter' || e.key === ' ') {
      handleClick(d);
    }
  }}
  onClick={() => handleClick(d)}
/>
```

### 5.2 ARIA Labels

**REGLA**: Agregar labels descriptivos para screen readers.

```javascript
<svg
  role="img"
  aria-label="Pipeline flow chart showing document processing stages"
>
  <title>Pipeline Flow Chart</title>
  <desc>A Sankey diagram showing documents flowing from Pending to OCR to Completed</desc>
  {/* Chart content */}
</svg>
```

### 5.3 Color + Pattern

**REGLA**: No usar solo color para transmitir información.

```javascript
// ✅ BIEN: Color + pattern
<rect
  fill={colorScale(d.status)}
  stroke={d.status === 'error' ? '#f44336' : 'none'}
  strokeWidth={d.status === 'error' ? 3 : 0}
  strokeDasharray={d.status === 'error' ? '5,5' : 'none'}
/>
```

